description:
Start your asteroid adventure! Get Star Birds on Steam: https://kgs.link/starbirds_ytka

Sources & further reading:
https://sites.google.com/view/sources-killer-asteroid/

Some killer asteroids were found only days before flyby. If they had struck Earth, the power of thousands of nuclear bombs would have flattened cities and killed millions. 
What if we spotted a 100-meter asteroid just two weeks before collision? Can humanity be saved?
